<TEXTAREA NAME="ReplyMessage" ROWS=10 COLS=45 WRAP="VIRTUAL">[QUOTE]Originally posted by Tinymouse:
[B]If you want to reproduce this bug, all you have to do is lose focus on the "Do you want a rez" window. 

For instance, I was looking through my inventory (using the "I" toggle) when a cleric rezzed me (with no warning, bad practice). I had to click out of the inventory window, which made the "Do you want a rez" window disappear. I suspect that the rez window was still there, just behind something (you couldn't see it of course). That might explain why you have to log out to get another rez cast (since the one is still 'waiting' for a yes or no).
[/B][/QUOTE]

</TEXTAREA>
